name: BoingBoingAlarm

”Alexa, wake me up at 7:00 AM to boing boing alarm tone”
”Alexa, set an alarm at 7:00 AM to boing boing alarm tone”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: boing boing alarm
des:
Hear three different boings and bounces in this crazy collection of sounds from your favorite cartoons! "Bouncy Ball," "Sproing Mornin'," and "Boink Stars."

Get Boing Boing Gold to unlock seven MORE bouncy-boingy alarms including: Stranger Twangs, Loco Pogo, Robo-Boing, Bungee Hump, Shake That Twang, I Gotta Bounce, and everyone's favorite...Sproing 2: The Final Bouncening! 

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you enjoyed Boing Boing Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next!
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
